15:25.210 --> 15:27.668
Yeah. Any tips for staying awake?

15:28.720 --> 15:32.088
Late in the epoch
of post-industrial capitalism.

15:32.220 --> 15:34.291
Oh, yeah. Yeah, yeah. That, too.

15:36.720 --> 15:37.710
See?

15:37.850 --> 15:38.840
Yeah.

15:40.100 --> 15:41.841
It's finally quiet enough to hear.

15:42.940 --> 15:44.476
-What?
-You hear it?

15:46.690 --> 15:48.180
-You hear it?
-No, I can't hear--

15:52.450 --> 15:55.192
The din of our suffering
drowns it out, but...

15:56.120 --> 15:59.499
here, in the silence
of death and ruin...

16:00.460 --> 16:03.418
you can hear the one thing
that history can't kill,

16:03.540 --> 16:05.588
the one thing that can never die.

16:06.630 --> 16:07.836
Hope.

16:07.960 --> 16:08.950
No.

16:09.670 --> 16:11.252
Hope died with truth.

16:12.050 --> 16:13.040
Listen.

16:20.390 --> 16:21.380
Yeah.

16:21.980 --> 16:24.051
-Yeah, it's a heart.
-Yeah. Yeah, yeah.

16:24.190 --> 16:25.726
Oh, my God. I can hear it.

16:25.860 --> 16:27.931
Yeah, the coeur de la bte.

16:28.070 --> 16:29.140
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

16:29.280 --> 16:31.817
-Yeah. What does that mean?
-"The heart of the beast."

16:31.950 --> 16:33.600
-"Heart of the beast."
-Yeah.

16:33.740 --> 16:37.233
-Is that from something, or is it...?
-Yeah, I read it somewhere. I forget.

16:38.030 --> 16:41.284
As for staying up all night, that's
really just a matter of willpower.

16:42.120 --> 16:43.110
And speed.

16:47.290 --> 16:48.837
Here come the nice.

16:51.340 --> 16:53.081
-Here.
-No, that's OK.

16:54.090 --> 16:55.797
Is there somewhere we can get coffee?

16:57.180 --> 16:58.295
No!

16:58.430 --> 17:00.216
Larry, just think about it.

17:00.640 --> 17:02.267
It might not be so bad.

17:02.730 --> 17:04.050
Assisted living?

17:05.690 --> 17:08.261
